08:11.070 --> 08:13.937
I DON'T KNOW--JUST--
COULD YOU JUST--

08:14.070 --> 08:16.868
COULD YOU COME LOOK AT IT?
COULD YOU COME OVER AND LOOK?

08:20.120 --> 08:24.591
AND I THINK WE'RE DOING
A PRE'ITY GOOD JOB.

08:24.740 --> 08:25.968
WE'RE GETTING THERE.

08:26.120 --> 08:27.985
I MEAN, WE DON'T HAVE
THE POT OF GOLD YET,

08:28.120 --> 08:30.429
AND YOU'RE NOT IN IT,
BUT...

08:30.570 --> 08:32.572
YOU KNOW,
I THINK IT'S A START.

08:37.200 --> 08:40.192
- I DON'T--
I DON'T KNOW.

08:50.940 --> 08:54.068
- ALL RIGHT,
HEY, HEY, THAT'S ENOUGH.

08:55.460 --> 08:58.179
LISTEN, MAX.

08:58.330 --> 09:01.561
