09:02.710 --> 09:04.678
- I'M EATING.

09:04.820 --> 09:09.052
- THE THING IS, MAX,
WE'RE PART OF A FAMILY.

09:09.200 --> 09:12.260
AND WHEN SOMETHING HAPPENS
TO SOMEBODY IN THE FAMILY,

09:12.410 --> 09:15.299
LIKE WHAT HAPPENED TO AMBER,
WE WANNA BE THERE FOR THEM.

09:15.450 --> 09:17.509
DOESN'T MATTER HOW HUNGRY
WE ARE OR HOW TIRED WE ARE.

09:17.660 --> 09:20.299
WE WANNA SHOW UP
FOR THE PERSON

09:20.450 --> 09:23.863
THAT'S HAVING TROUBLE.

09:24.010 --> 09:27.036
FAMILY'S THE MOST
IMPORTANT THING IN OUR LIVES.

09:27.180 --> 09:28.215
- MM-HMM.

09:29.670 --> 09:31.149
- SO...

09:31.290 --> 09:33.144
I THINK BECAUSE OF
SOME OF THE THINGS YOU SAID,

09:33.290 --> 09:36.498
IT WOULD BE NICE IF YOU
APOLOGIZED TO YOUR AUNT SARAH.

09:36.640 --> 09:38.255
- I DIDN'T
DO ANYTHING WRONG.

09:38.400 --> 09:42.018
YOU PROMISED ME THAT
WE COULD GO TO GET PANCAKES,

09:42.160 --> 09:46.051
