KEPT MAKING ME WAIT.

09:46.200 --> 09:48.680
- MAX, HAVE YOU EVER HEARD
OF THE WORD "EMPATHY?"

09:48.820 --> 09:50.822
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS?

09:50.960 --> 09:52.200
