WELL, IT MEANS

09:52.350 --> 09:54.136
THAT WE THINK ABOUT
OTHER PEOPLE'S FEELINGS

09:54.280 --> 09:56.748
WHEN WE DO THINGS--
NOT JUST OUR OWN.

09:56.900 --> 09:58.765
