THAT YOU STRUGGLE WITH

09:58.900 --> 10:00.140
BECAUSE OF YOUR ASPERGER'S.

10:00.280 --> 10:01.690
SO YOU'RE
NOT DOING ANYTHING WRONG,

10:01.840 --> 10:04.491
AND I JUST WANNA
HELP YOU LEARN EMPATHY.

10:04.630 --> 10:06.143
AND THAT'S WHY I THINK
