CARE ABOUT AMBER.

10:14.190 --> 10:16.363
- CAN I HAVE
MORE WHIPPED CREAM?

10:19.650 --> 10:21.333
- YEAH.

10:23.790 --> 10:24.757
- ALL RIGHT,
I MIGHT HAVE TO MISS

10:24.900 --> 10:26.094
